dataList.content: We're really getting to the climax now.
As I speak, two candidates have been consecutively eliminated!
The Shi caved the Wang's head right in as soon as he lost his final coin. What a dramatic double-knockout finish!
And in first place we still have... yes, Qiu of the Jia family!
W-who's that? Isn't he from the Jia family...?
We'll never defeat Jia Qiu anyway. Let's at least take Jia Baoyu out!
